message.text:
𝗧𝗔𝗠𝗥𝗔𝗗𝗜𝗢 | 𝗘𝗽𝗶𝘀𝗼𝗱𝗲 𝟭: 𝗧𝗮𝗺𝗛𝘂𝗻𝘁 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱

Day 2 of TamHunt 2025 at the FEU IHSN Student Council was filled with excitement and laughter as students shared their favorite moments in thy happy halls. 

The event brought together fresh energy and joyful stories, highlighting the strong sense of camaraderie in the organization, expectations, their interest to join the student council and more!

Host: Xancy Louise Cataquis
Interviewer: Christian James Bautista
Caption: Davonn Ashley Asuncion
Videographer: Al Carlo Borcena
Video Editor: Michelle Bacani

Day 2 of TamHunt 2025 at the FEU IHSN Student Council was filled with excitement and laughter as students shared their favorite moments in thy happy halls. 

The event brought together fresh energy and joyful stories, highlighting the strong sense of camaraderie in the organization, expectations, their interest to join the student council and more!

message.text:
𝗧𝗔𝗠𝗥𝗔𝗗𝗜𝗢 | 𝗘𝗽𝗶𝘀𝗼𝗱𝗲 𝟭: 𝗧𝗮𝗺𝗛𝘂𝗻𝘁 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱

Day 2 of TamHunt 2025 at the FEU IHSN Student Council was filled with excitement and laughter as students shared their favorite moments in thy happy halls. 

The event brought together fresh energy and joyful stories, highlighting the strong sense of camaraderie in the organization, expectations, their interest to join the student council and more!

Host: Xancy Louise Cataquis
Interviewer: Christian James Bautista
Caption: Davonn Ashley Asuncion
Videographer: Al Carlo Borcena
Video Editor: Michelle Bacani

#TamHunt2025
#CapiztahanSaRoxas
#FEUIHSNSC
#ForgeAhead
#IgnitedAndCentered

𝗧𝗔𝗠𝗥𝗔𝗗𝗜𝗢 | 𝗘𝗽𝗶𝘀𝗼𝗱𝗲 𝟭: 𝗧𝗮𝗺𝗛𝘂𝗻𝘁 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱

Day 2 of TamHunt 2025 at the FEU IHSN Student Council was filled with excitement and laughter as students shared their favorite moments in thy happy halls. 

The event brought together fresh energy and joyful stories, highlighting the strong sense of camaraderie in the organization, expectations, their interest to join the student council and more!

Host: Xancy Louise Cataquis
Interviewer: Christian James Bautista
Caption: Davonn Ashley Asuncion
Videographer: Al Carlo Borcena
Video Editor: Michelle Bacani

message.text:
Hello Tams! 💚 

This is your Matcha Girlie 🍵✨ bringing you authentic Japanese matcha drinks straight to campus! 🌸

From Classic Matcha Latte to White Chocolate Matcha Latte — we’ve got something to Matcha Your Mood 💖 

Smooth, creamy, and refreshing — perfect for study hours or just chilling with friends.

We’ve updated our menu, you can now choose your matcha level!! 🫶🏻

📩 DM me to pre-order and support your fellow Tam while treating yourself to happiness in a bottle! 
🌿

Order now for: September 15-16
Meet-up: FEU MANILA and UPAD

You can also check our FB page and IG Account.

IG: @YutoriMatchaPH
FB: Yutori Matcha PH

message.text:
Hello Tams! 💚 

This is your Matcha Girlie 🍵✨ bringing you authentic Japanese matcha drinks straight to campus! 🌸

From Classic Matcha Latte to White Chocolate Matcha Latte — we’ve got something to Matcha Your Mood 💖 

Smooth, creamy, and refreshing — perfect for study hours or just chilling with friends.

We’ve updated our menu, you can now choose your matcha level!! 🫶🏻

📩 DM me to pre-order and support your fellow Tam while treating yourself to happiness in a bottle! 
🌿

Order now for: September 15-16
Meet-up: FEU MANILA and UPAD

You can also check our FB page and IG Account.

IG: @YutoriMatchaPH
FB: Yutori Matcha PH
